      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know it's okay to not be okay but it doesn't feel okay. it feels permanent. like this hole in my chest is just how my life is now. every time i think about the future i just see a giant blank wall. there's no point in even trying to \"grieve\" or \"reach out\" when there's nothing left to save. it’s just exhausting... i'm just so tired of the pain.",
